{"tid":391973,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友好污糟。。。。","createTime":"2017-09-08T07:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T12:37:19.000Z","uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d12dc46be16d32d2d78fa1f0167755435cb60c8","tid":391973,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"女朋友個人衛生很差。。。用完紙巾球四圍掉，著完既襪仔會掉係地下，我忍唔住會成日幫佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有一樣。。。就係佢夜晚係唔刷牙！我叫佢刷牙，就好似呀爸捉個女去刷牙咁，佢琴晚仲要唔肯刷。。。佢仲要自豪話自己一日刷一次都唔會蛀牙（因為佢從來冇驗，冇牙痛就當自己冇蛀牙）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我試過有朋友同我講佢習慣都係夜晚唔刷牙，佢芳齡已經3x ，又係claim 自己棚牙好健康，但我心諗：你真係有口氣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想我女朋友會有好衛生習慣，點做呢？唔想成日叫佢做呢樣做個樣，我都覺得自己煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62db64ff0089096d48869e28925a165b98708392","tid":391973,"uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"3x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ab608e9ddb52e8b7e9f001eaefcc6533b60a4f","tid":391973,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"飛左佢啦"},{"pid":"0f8726404d16d5ae1f6e80e5c66c648102b9ccd3","tid":391973,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:34:18.000Z","msg":"fly"},{"pid":"ef4c8b89804c34ee819aea24029c7934bb4d80e7","tid":391973,"uid":142707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"我都係咁架<br />\n自我鐘意既人買左個電動牙刷比我<br />\n依家已經改左早晚刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而佢已經唔係我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2345c530369700e4944ac171702545a10345a9","tid":391973,"uid":22974,"like":0,"di